18d9i69 x1c1uobl x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz _a6hd" href="https://www.instagram.com/objectivecancer/p/C8i4jawASKc/" role="link" tabindex="0"><div class="_aagu"><div class="_aagv" style="padding-bottom: 133.333%;"><img alt="Today, we are talking about …🥁🥁… Colon Cancer! Topics we have covered: types of colon cancers, high risk symptoms, reliable support renounces, and important information about colon cancer that may help you or someone else you know. Did you know that colon cancer is the third most common type of cancer in the world and is the second leading cause of cancer-related deaths?? Stay informed and be proactive about your health. 

