g8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz _a6hd" href="https://www.instagram.com/objectivecancer/p/C6rWRVfLzB6/" role="link" tabindex="0"><div class="_aagu"><div class="_aagv" style="padding-bottom: 133.333%;"><img alt="Be proactive: here are ways to prevent and detect cancer early

Pay attention to your body. Are there anything changes? Any unexplained signs? Don’t let fear get in the way of verifying health. Don’t ignore the signs. Don’t hesitate to seek help. Embrace the prevention and detection tips. Cancer spreads fast and grows rapidly; verify and have it diagnosed before it is too late. Let’s prioritize our health and spread awareness together. 

Objective: Cancer, serves as an educational resource to inform and teach everyone about cancer.

