n></div><div class="_a9zr"><h2 class="x6s0dn4 x3nfvp2" tabindex="-1"><div class="html-div xdj266r xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x9f619 xjbqb8w x78zum5 x15mokao x1ga7v0g x16uus16 xbiv7yw x2fvf9 x1n2onr6 x1plvlek xryxfnj x1c4vz4f x2lah0s xdt5ytf xqjyukv x1qjc9v5 x1oa3qoh x1nhvcw1"><span class="xt0psk2"><span class="xjp7ctv"><div><a class="x1i10hfl xjqpnuy xc5r6h4 xqeqjp1 x1phubyo xdl72j9 x2lah0s x3ct3a4 xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak x2lwn1j xeuugli x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1ja2u2z x1t137rt x1q0g3np x1a2a7pz x6s0dn4 xjyslct x1ejq31n x18oe1m7 x1sy0etr xstzfhl x9f619 x1ypdohk x1f6kntn xl56j7k x17ydfre x2b8uid xlyipyv x87ps6o x14atkfc x5c86q x18br7mf x1i0vuye x11q7cde xr5sc7 xf8g3cd x20cjte xt0b8zv x568u83 xjbqb8w xr9e8f9 x1e4oeot x1ui04y5 x6en5u8 x972fbf x10w94by x1qhh985 x14e42zd xt0psk2 xt7dq6l xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x1n2onr6 x1n5bzlp" href="https://www.instagram.com/objectivecancer/" role="link" tabindex="0">objectivecancer</a></div></span></span></div></h2><div class="xt0psk2"><h1 class="_ap3a _aaco _aacu _aacx _aad7 _aade" dir="auto">Today marks World Ovarian Cancer Day!<br><br>What even is ovarian cancer…? Ovarian cancer is a type of cancer that forms in female ovaries. It is usually diagnosed during the later stages which makes it more challenging to treat. Early detection and treatment are crucial for improving outcomes. Reach out to a healthcare professional soon to be safe. <br><br>Studies have shown that not many women know about Ovarian Cancer. According to the American Cancer Society, a women’s risk of Ovarian Cancer is about 1 in 87, and her chances of dying from it is about 1 in 130. Furthermore, the World Ovarian Cancer Coalition has projected that by 2050, the number of women around the world with Ovarian Cancer will rise over 55% leading to 503,448 diagnosed. This shows how women are being left behind in the race for health. The more likely a woman knows about these risks and conditions the more likely she will get herself tested. Reach out to healthcare providers if you can have a diagnostic test, like a Rectovaginal pelvic exam, a transvaginal ultrasound, or a CA-125 blood test if you have any unexplained signs or symptoms of ovarian cancer. It is best to be tested and have it confirmed, rather than not! <br><br>The World Ovarian Cancer Day is a global campaign that raises awareness about Ovarian Cancer and its impact on women’s health worldwide. Supporters around the world aim to reduce the number of deaths in women caused by Ovarian Cancer through increased awareness and action. It first starts with knowing the main symptoms and detecting it early. Gain the knowledge, spread it, and save lives. Raise awareness so that no woman will be left behind!<br><br>Objective: Cancer - serves as an educational resource to inform and learn about cancer.<br><br>Follow for more! 🎗️<br><a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n x18oe1m7 x1sy0etr xstzfhl x972fbf x10w94by x1qhh985 x14e42zd x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 x3ct3a4 xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz  _aa9_ _a6hd" href="https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/cancerawareness/" role="link" tabindex="0">#cancerawareness</a> <a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n x18oe1m7 x1sy0etr xstzfhl x972fbf x10w94by x1qhh985 x14e42zd x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 x3ct3a4 xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz  _aa9_ _a6hd" href="https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/cancerresearch/" role="link" tabindex="0">#cancerresearch</a> <a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n x18oe1m7 x1sy0etr xstzfhl x972fbf x10w94by x1qhh985 x14e42zd x9f619 x1ypdohk xt0psk2 x3ct3a4 xdj266r x14z9mp xat24cr x1lziwak xexx8yu xyri2b x18d9i69 x1c1uobl x16tdsg8 x1hl2dhg xggy1nq x1a2a7pz  _aa9_ _a6hd" href="https://www.instagram.com/explore/tags/cancer/" role="link" tabindex="0">#cancer</a> <a class="x1i10hfl xjbqb8w x1ejq31n x18oe1m7 x1sy0etr xstzfhl x972fbf x10w94by x1qhh985 x14e42zd 